Amashuri nize: 
1. Nize amashuri y'inshuke.

column104: Yego, interuro "Abashumba barya ibitoki" irakwiriye ku gihe buri munsi, kuko igaragaza igikorwa gihoraho cyangwa gisubirwamo.

column110:
Naho waba ushaka kuvuga "buri gitondo", interuro "Abahungu bavuga ko hanze hijimye" yakosorwa cyangwa ikavugwa ku buryo bukurikira:

"Abahungu bavuga ko hanze haza umwijima." (bivuga ko bibaye cyangwa bigiye kuba mu gitondo cyabayeho).

"Abahungu bavuga ko hanze hijimye" birakunze, ariko bikaba ntibigera kubihura neza nk'uburyo bwo kuvuga mu gihe kigezweho.
column122: Iyi nteruro irashoboka kandi irumvikana neza mu gihe umuntu avuga ko buri gitondo, abana baba babyina. Ibi bitanga igitekerezo cyo kuvuga ko ibikorwa bibera kenshi kandi buri munsi mu gitondo.
column137: Interuro "Abahungu barambwira ngo, 'turarushye'" ntabwo ihuye neza n'igihe buri mugoroba, kuko "barambwira" igomba kuvugwa mu buryo bw'igihe gihoraho. Uko wakosora ni ukureba igihe gikwiye, urugero "barimo kumbwira" cyangwa kugirana imvugo ijyanye n'igihe gihoraho.
column140: Iyi nteruro "Abagore baravuga ngo, 'igihe kirageze cyo gusinzira'" ni nziza kandi ikwiye, kuko "baravuga" yerekana igikorwa cyo kuvuga kibera buri munsi (buri gihe), kandi "buri munsi" ifasha kumvikanisha ko ibyo bikorwa bibera buri munsi.
column146: Iyi nteruro ni nziza, kandi irahuye neza n'imikoreshereze ya -ra- mu gihe cy'imigenzo cyangwa ibikorwa bisanzwe bikorwa buri gitondo.
column155: Interuro "Abasore baririmba indirimbo" ni nziza kandi ihuye n'igihe aka kanya, kuko "baririmba" ivuga igikorwa kiri kuba mu gihe nyir’izina.
column158: Interuro "Aka kanya, abagore basoma" ni nziza, kuko "basoma" yerekana igikorwa kiri kuba mu gihe cy’ako kanya. Iyi nteruro ikora neza muri konteksti y'igihe cyo kuvuga ibiri kuba ubu.
column161: Iyi nteruro yakosorwa ikaba "Abanyeshuri bambwira ko hanze haza umwijima" cyangwa "Abanyeshuri bambwira ko hanze hari umwijima." Izi nteruro zavuga ko igikorwa kiri kuba muri ako kanya (haza umwijima), kandi bihura n'igihe nyacyo cy'ako kanya.
column164: nteruro "Abana bavuga ngo, 'igihe kirageze cyo gusinzira'" ni nziza, kuko "bavuga" isobanura igikorwa kiri kuba muri aka kanya, aho abana bari kuvuga icyo kintu muri icyo gihe.
column182: Interuro "Nsanga abanyeshuri baririmba" ntabwo ihuye neza n'igihe mu kanya, kuko "baririmba" ivuga igikorwa kigiye kuba cyangwa kimaze kuba. Icyo wakora ni gukoresha "barimo kuririmba" kugira ngo byumvikane ko igikorwa kiri kuba muri icyo gihe nyir’izina.
column188: Iyi nteruro nakoresha iyo nari kuvuga ibikorwa bibera muri iki gihe runaka, gusa "boga" ntabwo iba yerekana ibyo mu buryo bukwiye mu gihe cyo kuvuga ibikorwa biri kuba. Iyo umuntu avuga "aba ni abakozi bari kogosha", bihura neza n'igihe kiri kuba ubu.
column191: yi nteruro ni nziza, kuko "aka kanya" ikwiranye n'igihe cyihariye, kandi "baraboha amajipo" isobanura igikorwa kiri kuba muri icyo gihe. Ibi byumvikana neza nk'uko byakabaye mu gihe umuntu avuga ibyo ari gukora muri ako kanya
column197: Interuro "Abagore bararirimba" ni nziza kandi ihuye n'igihe aka kanya, kuko "bararirimba" ivuga igikorwa kiri kuba mu gihe nyir’izina.
column206: Iyi nteruro "Abasore baravuga ko igihe kirageze cyo gutaha" ni nziza kandi ikwiriye, kuko "baravuga" yerekana igikorwa kiri kuba muri uwo mwanya, kandi "aka kanya" ivuga ko igikorwa kirimo kuba muri icyo gihe nyir’izina.
column215: Yego, interuro "Abantu ntibarasukura" irakwiriye ku gihe aka kanya, kuko igaragaza neza ko abantu batari gusukura muri uwo mwanya.
column227: Yego, interuro "Aba ni abagabo bararirimba" irakwiriye ku gihe aka kanya, kuko igikorwa cyo kuririmba kiri kuba nonaha.
column239: Interuro ya mbere "bari kumbwira" ifite imikoreshereze ya -ra- ishobora kugaragaza igikorwa cyabaye mbere, ariko "aka kanya" isaba gukoresha inshinga ikora ku gikorwa kiri kuba muri icyo gihe nyacyo. Iyo igikorwa kiri kuba ubu, byaba byiza gukoresha "barimo kumbwira", kuko "barimo" yerekana igikorwa kiri gukorwa mu gihe nyacyo.
column242:
Kugira ngo iyi nteruro ijyane n'igihe cya aka kanya, wakoresha inshinga ikora ku gikorwa kiri kuba muri ako kanya. Urugero rwiza rw'uko byakosorwa ni:

"Abakobwa barimo kuvuga ngo, 'igihe kirageze cyo gusinzira.'"
(Ibi byerekana ko abakobwa bari kuvuga muri icyo gihe nyir'izina.)

"Abakobwa baravuga ngo, 'igihe kirageze cyo gusinzira.'"
(Iyi nayo yakwiriye, kuko baravuga ivuga igikorwa kiri kuba muri icyo gihe.)
column248:
Interuro "Aba ni abashumba bari guteka" yashobora gukosorwa mu buryo bukurikira kugira ngo bihure n'igihe nyacyo:

"Aba ni abashumba barimo guteka."
(Ibi byaba bivuze ko abashumba bari guteka muri aka kanya.)

"Aba ni abashumba batangiye guteka."
(Iyi nteruro nayo yakwiriye kuko isobanura ko abashumba bari guteka muri uwo mwanya.)
column251: Iyi nteruro "Nsanga abasore bari gusukura" ifite imikoreshereze ya -ra- itabereye aka kanya, kuko igikorwa "bari gusukura" ntikiri mu gihe nyir’izina.
